commit_message: Close manually created channels to avoid deadlock.
Correct bug in BWA index path. Schedule mapReads jobs to long-sl7 queue.
Correct bug in main.nf: files in sets were included as literals and Nextflow did not make symbolic links.
Update Dockerfile to install samtools. Changed container name.
Correct typo in bwa call. Update cluster to meet crg requirements.
Change to SRA-tools to download fastq files. Remove colortobase compilation, assuming Docker use.
SGE queue info moved to nextflow.config.
Made workaround to avoid Univa crash because tags contain '/'.
Corrected more typos in cluster config profile.
Corrected typo in cluster config profile.
